    return np.random.rand(*bins.shape) * np.exp(item / bins) + np.sin(np.pi * item / bins)
```

### Implementation 7: Conditional Best Fit

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    if item > bins:
        return -np.inf
    return np.exp(item - bins) * np.std(bins) + np.sin(np.pi * item / bins)
