### Implementation 8: Hyperbolic Fit

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.tanh(item / bins) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.log(item + np.mean(bins))
```

### Implementation 9: Utilization-Based Priority

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.exp(item / bins) * (item * np.std(bins)) + np.sin(np.pi * item / bins)
```

### Implementation 10: Mean Minimization

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.exp(item - bins) * np.mean(bins) + np.sin(np.pi * item / bins)
```

